SudoAskPass is a graphical sudo password prompt application built using GNUstep
for FreeBSD systems. It provides a clean, simple interface for entering sudo
passwords when using the SUDO_ASKPASS environment variable.

Features:
- Clean graphical interface using GNUstep
- Secure password input field
- Keyboard shortcuts support (Enter/Escape)
- Floating window that stays on top
- Full compatibility with sudo's SUDO_ASKPASS mechanism
